      <title>纽约州在民事欺诈审判中向特朗普索赔 3.7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约总检察长表示，唐纳德·特朗普及其公司十多年来在财务文件中夸大其资产价值，应被责令从 2.5 亿美元罚款 3.7 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普聘请德克萨斯州堕胎法背后的律师进行最高法院选票斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州为期六周的堕胎法允许普通公民向违法者寻求 10,000 美元的赏金，该法背后的律师已被唐纳德·特朗普聘请，帮助他的美国最高法院争取留在总统选票上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/trump-ballot-fight-at-supreme-court-led-by-texan-behind-abortion-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登支持提供 1.89 亿美元贷款，用激光发现甲烷泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-backs-189-million-loan-to-spot-methane-leaks-with-lasers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府支持向科罗拉多州博尔德的一家公司提供 1.89 亿美元的贷款承诺，用于开发庞大的甲烷检测网络，旨在使用激光监测数以万计的石油和天然气站点，以识别强效吸热剂的泄漏。天然气是造成气候变化的主要因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-backs-189-million-loan-to-spot-methane-leaks-with-lasers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰岛渔业部长因 2023 年捕鲸禁令受到谴责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/iceland-fisheries-minister-rebuked-over-2023-whaling-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冰岛渔业部长斯万迪斯·斯瓦瓦尔斯多蒂尔（Svandis Svavarsdottir）因去年夏天突然实施捕鲸禁令而导致捕鲸季的大部分时间停止，因此受到该国监察员的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/iceland-fisheries-minister-rebuked-over-2023-whaling-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>萨默斯敦促首席执行官们拒绝特朗普，称选举是二战以来最重要的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/summers-urges-ceos-to-reject-trump-in-most-vital-vote-since-wwii</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前财政部长劳伦斯·萨默斯呼吁美国商界领袖放下对拜登政府过度进步政策的担忧，并认识到唐纳德·特朗普连任总统所面临的历史性危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/summers-urges-ceos-to-reject-trump-in-most-vital-vote-since-wwii</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:43:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
