      <title>美国准备就胡塞武装红海袭击做出高风险决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/houthi-red-sea-attacks-us-retaliation-may-inflame-tensions-experts-warn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其盟国在告诉也门胡塞武装分子要么停止袭击红海船只，要么面临未具体说明的行动后，正在考虑对他们进行打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/houthi-red-sea-attacks-us-retaliation-may-inflame-tensions-experts-warn</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:29:19 GMT</pubDate>
